                            "value": "<b>Mosunmola “Mo” Abudu</b> (Nigeria), a media entrepreneur and philanthropist, is the CEO of EbonyLife Media. She hosts the pan-African talk show <i>Moments with Mo</i> and is the founder of the Inspire Africa Foundation."
